target_effect: Affective coherence increased cognitive complexity in participant-generated narratives compared to affective incoherence.

target_effect: Ps believed confederate's expressions were happier than their private feelings, but only in vulnerable conditions.

target_effect: Ps own responsiveness was a significant predictor of their perception of their partners' responsiveness.
